message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
IABF Tamaraws, MarkProf Batch 22 Awaits You! ✨

The FEU IABF Student Council, through the STRAW External Affairs, in partnership with MarkProf Foundation, Inc., proudly invites you to the MarkProf Bootcamp Roadshow on September 21, 2025 (7:00 PM – 8:30 PM).

For two decades, MarkProf has been shaping future leaders—training over 500 top students who now lead in market innovation and nation-building across major organizations. Each year, hundreds of applicants nationwide aspire to join the prestigious free 8-weekend Marketing and Sales Bootcamp—but only 25 young marketing leaders make it through the rigorous selection process.

Don’t miss this chance to learn more about the MarkProf journey and get tips on how to ace the application process from MarkProf alumni themselves.

Join the event here: https://bit.ly/MP22Online

#SoaringGreaterHeights
